    <item>
      <title>欧尔班下台可能会缓解匈牙利与欧盟的紧张关系</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/13/world/europe/hungary-eu-orban-magyar.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理维克托·欧尔班多年来一直阻碍欧盟，尤其是最近几个月。彼得·马扎尔（Peter Magyar）的当选可能会改变这一点，但幅度有限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/13/world/europe/hungary-eu-orban-magyar.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 04:00:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>谁是彼得·马扎尔（Peter Magyar），推翻匈牙利欧尔班的人</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/12/world/europe/who-peter-magyar-hungary-election-opposition-orban.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马扎尔在匈牙利选举中取得成功，很大程度上是由于公众对腐败的普遍愤怒以及对经济增长乏力的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/12/world/europe/who-peter-magyar-hungary-election-opposition-orban.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 03:01:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>这个匈牙利小镇解释了为什么欧尔班可能会在周日失败</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/10/world/europe/hungary-corruption-orban-magyar-election.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴拉顿湖作为度假胜地深受人们喜爱。现在，豪华房地产项目服务于总理欧尔班·维克托的许多朋友，当地人已经厌倦了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/10/world/europe/hungary-corruption-orban-magyar-election.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 03:00:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加州民主党人急忙支持埃里克·斯瓦尔韦尔，但很快就抛弃了他</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/12/us/california-democrats-eric-swalwell.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华盛顿州众议员埃里克·斯瓦尔韦尔（Eric Swalwell）在加州议会大厦内鲜为人知。但在他被公开指控性侵犯之前几周，有影响力的团体就开始支持他竞选州长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/12/us/california-democrats-eric-swalwell.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 01:01:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃里克·斯瓦尔韦尔因性侵犯指控而暂停加州州长竞选活动</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/12/us/eric-swalwell-suspends-california-governor-campaign.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该代表在社交媒体帖子中表示，他“对过去做出的判断错误深感抱歉”，但承诺将打击他所谓的“虚假指控”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/12/us/eric-swalwell-suspends-california-governor-campaign.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 01:00:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
